Cisco ASR 1000 SNMP MIB Support List

The following list indicates the MIBs that are supported by ASR1K Routers. SNMP version 1 MIBs are in the v1 directory and SNMP version 2 MIBs are in the v2 directory. Note that for almost every MIB .my file in the v2 directory, there exists a SNMP version 1 conversion of the MIB -V1SMI.my file in the v1 directory. MIBs are categorized into three types: Supported and Verified MIBs, Supported and Unverified MIBs, and Unsupported MIBs.

These MIBS are supported on Cisco IOS XE 3S and on Cisco IOS XE 16 software images.

    • ENTITY-MIB (RFC 4133)

    • CISCO-IETF-PW-MIB

Note: Refer to Cisco ASR 1K MIB Specification Guide for more information.

    • CISCO-RTTMON-IP-EXT-MIB

    • ENTITY-STATE-MIB
    • CISCO-DSP-MGMT-MIB
  • Removed the following MIBS from Unsupported List:
    • ENTITY-STATE-TC-MIB
  • Added the following MIBS to Unsupported List:
    • CISCO-DOT3-OAM-MIB
    • CISCO-VOICE-IF-MIB
    • CISCO-VOICE-ANALOG-IF-MIB
    • CISCO-CALL-APPLICATION-MIB
  • Updated MIB revision:
    • CISCO-RTTMON-MIB from 200903230000Z to 201006110000Z

  • CISCO-RTTMON-MIB - Version changed from 200701260000Z to 200803240000Z.
  • CISCO-VPDN-MGMT-MIB - Version changed from 200601200000Z to 200705070000Z.
  • CISCO-IPMROUTE-MIB - Version changed from 200503070000Z to 200804010000Z.
  • CISCO-IGMP-FILTER-MIB - Moved from Unsupported List to Supported and Verified List.
  • CISCO-IETF-FRR-MIB and MPLS-TE-MIB - Moved from Unsupported List to Supported and Unverified List.
  • CISCO-SLB-EXT-MIB and CISCO-SLB-MIB - Moved from Supported and Verified List to Unsupported List.
  • Added the following MIBS to Supported and Verified List:
    • ATM-MIB
    • CISCO-AAL5-MIB
    • CISCO-ATM-EXT-MIB
    • CISCO-ATM-PVCTRAP-EXTN-MIB

    • CISCO-IETF-PW-MPLS-MIB
    • MPLS-L3VPN-STD-MIB
  • Added the following MIBS to Supported and Unverified List:
    • ATM-FORUM-ADDR-REG
    • ATM-FORUM-MIB
    • CISCO-ATM-QOS-MIB
  • Added the following MIBS to Unsupported List:
